{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for button component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the button component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","","        override var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","","        override var borderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMd }","","        override var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["    OrangeTheme(button: CustomButtonComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, borders, colors and space semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let buttonComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider","                                                spaces: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider())"]},{"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.9.0"}]}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeButtonComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","title":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of buttons"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"ButtonComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"buttons"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text